"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The health minister said doctors are trying to catch up with the virus because they were slow to find it. There are hundreds of suspected cases in central Africa, but experts think the real number might be much higher.\",            \"english_title\": \"Virus in Central Africa\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ministro de salud dijo que los doctores est\u00e1n tratando de alcanzar al virus porque fueron lentos en encontrarlo. Hay cientos de casos sospechosos en \u00c1frica central, pero los expertos piensan que el n\u00famero real podr\u00eda ser mucho mayor.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Virus en \u00c1frica Central\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Estonia thinks a drone was a Ukrainian missile that got off course because of Russian electronic interference.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estonia piensa que un dron era un misil ucraniano que se desvi\u00f3 por interferencia electr\u00f3nica rusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Dron\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Afghanistan, three out of four people cannot meet their basic needs today.\",            \"english_title\": \"Needs in Afghanistan\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Afganist\u00e1n, tres de cada cuatro personas no pueden cubrir sus necesidades b\u00e1sicas hoy.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Necesidades en Afganist\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Some 750 firefighters are fighting uncontrolled fires with the help of helicopters that drop water.\",            \"english_title\": \"Firefighters Battle Fires\",            \"translated_version\": \"Unos 750 bomberos est\u00e1n luchando contra incendios descontrolados con la ayuda de helic\u00f3pteros que tiran agua.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Bomberos Luchan Contra Incendios\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Abstract Expressionist's painting, Number 7A, 1948, is now his most expensive artwork ever sold at auction.\",            \"english_title\": \"Expensive Painting Sold\",            \"translated_version\": \"La pintura del Expresionista Abstracto, N\u00famero 7A, 1948, es ahora su obra de arte m\u00e1s cara vendida en una subasta.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pintura Cara Vendida\"        }    ]}"